0x8074CC1886802912// SetHeliResistToExplosion
void SET_HELI_RESIST_TO_EXPLOSION(Vehicle helicopter, BOOL bResistToExplosion);Parameters:helicopter: The helicopter to apply resistance to.bResistToExplosion: Set to true to make the helicopter resistant to explosions, or false to disable this resistance.Makes a helicopter resistant to multiple explosions. When enabled, helicopters can survive two or more explosions.NativeDB Introduced: 2545
